Description: Two joining shoulder fragments of Attic black-figure painted pottery neck-amphora. Part of helmet, hand and spiral pattern. Purple for alternate tongues and on crest of helmet.
Bibliographic references: CVA British Museum 8 / Corpus Vasorum Antiquorum: Great Britain 13, British Museum 8 (Pl. GB 608, 18)
Weber 2012 / Untersuchungen zur archaischen griechischen Keramik aus anderen ägyptischen Fundorten (TD 58)
